'''額我略三世·拉罕'''（{{Lang-ar|غريغوريوس الثالث لحام}}；{{lang-la|Gregorius III Lahamus}}；{{lang-en|Gregory III Laham}}：{{bd|1933年|12月15日||}}），本名'''盧特菲·拉罕'''（{{lang-en|Lutfy Laham}}）<ref name="cathhier"/>是[[默基特希臘禮天主教安提約基雅宗主教區|默基特希臘禮天主教安提約基雅宗主教區榮休宗主教]]，他於2017年5月6日榮休。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Dalle Chiese Orientali, 06.05.2017 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2017/05/06/0303/00682.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721112844/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2017/05/06/0303/00682.html |archivedate=2019-07-21 |language=it |date=2017-05-06}}</ref>

==著作==
額我略三世宗主教曾編著不少書籍，包括

*''Introduction to the Liturgical Services and their Symbols in the Eastern Church''
*''The Voice of the Shepherd - Eastern Liturgical Spirituality''
*''Life of Archbishop {{link-en|耶爾馬諾斯·亞當|Germanos Adam|Germanos Adam}}''
*''History of the Melkite Church ''翻譯本（英語及德語）
*''The Melkite Greek Catholic Church at the Second Vatican Council''

